                "caption": "Figure 1:Precision-sensitive GUI tasks expose a capability gap hidden by conventional GUI benchmarks.\nIn region-tolerant interaction, nearby pixels inside the same interface component lead to the same state transition.\nIn precise geometric construction, an action targets a point on a continuous canvas; small coordinate errors alter geometric constraints and propagate through dependent objects.",
